<view class="page">
  <view class="contact-hero card">
    <text class="h1">联系 GeoGi 顾问</text>
    <text class="lead">需要确认诊断范围、交付周期或资料填写方式，可以先联系顾问沟通。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section info-card card">
    <text class="info-title">企业微信</text>
    <text class="info-copy">{{wechatId}}</text>
    <text class="info-hint">复制后可在微信中搜索添加。正式发布时可替换为企业微信二维码原图。</text>
    <button class="primary-button copy-button" bindtap="copyWechat">复制企业微信</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section info-card card">
    <text class="info-title">邮箱</text>
    <text class="info-copy">{{email}}</text>
    <button class="secondary-button copy-button" bindtap="copyEmail">复制邮箱</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section info-card card">
    <text class="info-title">工作时间</text>
    <text class="info-copy">{{workHours}}</text>
    <button class="secondary-button copy-button" bindtap="goDiagnosis">提交品牌诊断资料</button>
  </view>
</view>
